Package com.googlecode.cqengine.resultset.filter

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DeduplicatingIterator<O,A>
    An iterator which wraps another, to suppress duplicate objects, where a duplicate object is one which has the same value(s) for the given attribute.
    DeduplicatingResultSet<O,A>
    A ResultSet which wraps another, to suppress duplicate objects, where a duplicate object is one which has the same value(s) for the given attribute.
    FilteringIterator<O>
    An Iterator which wraps another iterator, and for each object returned by the wrapped iterator, calls an FilteringIterator.isValid(Object, com.googlecode.cqengine.query.option.QueryOptions) method.
    FilteringResultSet<O>
    A ResultSet which wraps an Iterable and which calls an abstract FilteringResultSet.isValid(Object, com.googlecode.cqengine.query.option.QueryOptions) method for each object.
    MaterializedDeduplicatedIterator<O>
    An iterator which wraps another and prevents duplicate objects from being returned.
    QuantizedResultSet<O>
    An implementation of FilteringResultSet which filters objects based on whether they match a given query.
